verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
I'm not gonna settle for anything less.
God has given me the best.
So I'll take it, and receive it, by faith.
And when the enemy comes around;
he's the one who's gonna be bound.
For God's given all power to me.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
There are no chains that now can bind me.
There is nothing that can hold me down.
So when the enemy comes around;
he's the one who's gonna be bound.
For God's given all power to me.
